</div><div class="indent"><strong>Schlock</strong>: I didn't grab the shotgun. <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/PreAssKickingOneLiner" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/PreAssKickingOneLiner">I grabbed the short-barrel rotary fifty and six cases of ammo</a>.
</div><div class="indent"><strong>Footnote</strong>: "The rotating barrel assembly on the Strohl Munitions Short-barrel handcannon may give the user a wicked pinch if the weapon is held incorrectly. This makes it an unpopular selection for many military forces. Also, it can be configured to send <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/MoreDakka" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/MoreDakka">anywhere between five hundred and five thousand projectiles per minute downrange with great accuracy</a>, making it an exceedingly unpopular selection for the enemies of many military forces."
